About Pudhupettai

Pudhupettai (transl. New Hood/Area) is a 2006 Indian Tamil-language gangster film written and directed by Selvaraghavan. The film stars his brother Dhanush in the lead role, with Sneha and Sonia Agarwal as the female leads. The music is scored by Yuvan Shankar Raja, and the cinematography is by Arvind Krishna.

Directed by: Selvaraghavan
Produced by: K. Muralidharan, V. Swaminathan & G. Venugopal
Screenplay by: Selvaraghavan, Balakumaran (Dialogue)
Story by: Selvaraghavan
Starring: Dhanush, Sneha, Sonia Agarwal
Music by: Yuvan Shankar Raja
Cinematography: Arvind Krishna
Edited by: Kola Bhaskar
Production Company: Lakshmi Movie Makers

ytdata.title: Microsoft's Move To Snapdragon ARM Processors From Intel & AMD: Windows PCs To Get Costlier?
ytdata.description: Snapdragon introduces a new generation of processor for Microsoft devices which will run on ARM based architecture. Apple has recently moved from Intel's x86 based architecture to the M series of processors. For long, people have used Intel and AMD's x86 based chips for their PCs. But now, Microsoft is likely to take the same route as Apple in its conference on 20th May. Will this Qualcomm Snapdragon X Elite ARM Chip increase the cost? What will happen to the x86 systems? We explain. #Microsoft #Qualcomm #Snapdragon

ytdata.title: Manmadhan | Thathai Thathai | Silambarasan, Jyotika | Yuvan Shankar Raja
ytdata.description:
We all love a bit of throwback in life! Presenting #ThinkTapes ⏪ rewinding you to the best of 90s & 2000s music. Here is the much-loved 'Thathai Thathai' video song from Manmadhan - A Yuvan Shankar Raja Musical!!

#Manmadhan is a 2004 Indian Tamil-language romantic thriller film directed and written by A. J. Murugan with dialogues by Balakumaran. #Silambarasan played dual roles for the first time in his career while #Jyotika, Sindhu Tolani, Santhanam, Atul Kulkarni, and Goundamani played supporting roles. The film's score and soundtrack are composed by #YuvanShankarRaja.

Song: Thathai Thathai
Singers: STR, Blaaze, Vasundara Das
Lyrics: Vaali

All Songs Composed by Yuvan Shankar Raja
